					</ol>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>

		<div class="wrapper">
			<section>
				<h4 class="section-title">
					How it Works (as the photographer)
				</h4>
				<div class="content">
					<ol>
						<li>
							Photographer creates Candid9 account and creates
							batch of 25 Photo Sessions.
						</li>
						<li>
							Photographer prints out 25 Candid9 tickets, each has
							a unique QR Code that points to a Photo Session.
						</li>
						<li>
